theorem ex8 (n m k : Nat) (h : Nat.succ n + m = Nat.succ n + k) : Nat.succ (n + m) = Nat.succ (n + k) :=
Nat.succ_add .. ▸ Nat.succ_add .. ▸ h
theorem ex9 (a b : Nat) (h₁ : a = a + b) (h₂ : a = b) : a = b + a  :=
h₂ ▸ h₁
theorem ex10 (a b : Nat) (h : a = b) : b = a :=
h ▸ rfl
